#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:2
msgid "Releasing your OpenMV Cam Scripts for Production"
msgstr "发布您的OpenMV Cam脚本以供生产使用"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:4
msgid ""
"Once you've got your OpenMV Cam Scripts working like you want and you are"
" ready to ship your product powered by OpenMV you need to freeze your "
"scripts into the firmware. To do this you will need to compile our "
"firmware. Luckily, thanks to GitHub actions you can do this in the cloud "
"without having to install our build system."
msgstr ""
"一旦您的 OpenMV Cam 脚本按照您的要求工作，并且您准备好使用 OpenMV "
"驱动的产品，您需要将您的脚本固化到固件中。为此，您需要编译我们的固件。幸运的是，由于 GitHub "
"的存在，您可以在云端进行此操作，而无需安装我们的构建系统。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:9
msgid ""
"For power users, we recommend setting up our firmware development "
"environment so you can build the firmware from the source. See how to do "
"so `here <https://github.com/openmv/openmv/blob/master/src/README.md>`_."
msgstr ""
"对于高级用户，我们建议设置我们的固件开发环境，以便您可以从源代码构建固件。请参阅 `here "
"<https://github.com/openmv/openmv/blob/master/src/README.md>`_ 了解如何操作。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:12
msgid ""
"For everyone else, you can use GitHub actions. To do so, follow the below"
" steps:"
msgstr "对于其他用户，您可以使用GitHub 操作。要这样做，请按照以下步骤操作："

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:14
msgid "Get a GitHub account if you don't already have one."
msgstr "如果您还没有GitHub账户，请注册一个GitHub账户。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:15
msgid "Fork the OpenMV firmware `repo <https://github.com/openmv/openmv>`_."
msgstr "Fork OpenMV 固件 `repo <https://github.com/openmv/openmv>`_。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:16
msgid "Enable GitHub actions on your fork."
msgstr "在您的fork上启用GitHub操作。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:18
msgid ""
"After doing this, you can then edit files online in GitHub and your fork "
"will automatically build a new firmware image for your OpenMV Cam."
msgstr "完成以上操作后，您可以在 GitHub 上在线编辑文件，您的 Fork 将自动构建一个新的固件映像用于您的 OpenMV Cam。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:22
msgid "How to freeze your scripts"
msgstr "如何固化您的脚本"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:24
msgid ""
"The process of freezing scripts into the firmware ensures that your code "
"cannot be edited by your end-users. Best of all, it means that your code "
"will run without needing any files on the internal flash and/or SD card. "
"Additionally, any files on the internal flash or SD card will be "
"overridden by what scripts you freeze that have the same name."
msgstr ""
"将脚本固化到固件中的过程可以确保您的代码不能被最终用户编辑。最重要的是，这意味着您的代码将在不需要内部闪存和/或 SD "
"卡上的任何文件的情况下运行。此外，任何位于内部闪存或 SD 卡上的文件将被您固化的脚本覆盖。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:29
msgid "Anyway, to freeze scripts you simply need to do the following:"
msgstr "无论如何，要固化脚本，您只需要执行以下操作："

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:31
msgid ""
"Add your custom scripts to the `libraries folder "
"<https://github.com/openmv/openmv/tree/master/scripts/libraries>`_."
msgstr ""
"将您的自定义脚本添加到 `libraries folder "
"<https://github.com/openmv/openmv/tree/master/scripts/libraries>`_。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:32
msgid ""
"Rename your ``main.py`` script to ``boot.py`` so that it runs first "
"before anything else."
msgstr "将您的 ``main.py`` 脚本重命名为 ``boot.py``，以便在其他任何操作之前首先运行它。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:33
msgid ""
"Determine which `board folder "
"<https://github.com/openmv/openmv/tree/master/src/omv/boards>`_ "
"corresponds to your OpenMV Cam."
msgstr ""
"确定哪个 `board folder <https://github.com/openmv/openmv/tree/master/src/omv/b"
"oards>`_ 对应于您的 OpenMV Cam。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:36
msgid "OPENMV2 -> OpenMV Cam M4."
msgstr "OPENMV2 -> OpenMV Cam M4。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:37
msgid "OPENMV3 -> OpenMV Cam M7."
msgstr "OPENMV3 -> OpenMV Cam M7。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:38
msgid "OPENMV4 -> OpenMV Cam H7."
msgstr "OPENMV4 -> OpenMV Cam H7。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:39
msgid "OPENMV4P -> OpenMV Cam H7 Plus."
msgstr "OPENMV4P -> OpenMV Cam H7 Plus。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:40
msgid "Everything else should be straight forwards."
msgstr "其他都应该很直接。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:42
msgid ""
"Edit the ``manifest.py`` file for your board type to include your "
"scripts. If you just have one script then this should at minimum include "
"you adding ``freeze (\"$(OMV_LIB_DIR)/\", \"boot.py\")`` to the "
"``manifest.py`` file."
msgstr ""
"编辑与您的板型对应的 ``manifest.py`` 文件，以包含您的脚本。如果您只有一个脚本，那么至少应将 ``freeze "
"(\"$(OMV_LIB_DIR)/\", \"boot.py\")`` 添加到 ``manifest.py`` 文件中。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:45
msgid "Compile the code and generate the firmware image for your OpenMV Cam."
msgstr "编译代码并为您的OpenMV Cam生成固件映像。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:47
msgid ""
"Once you flash this new firmware image to your OpenMV Cam it will "
"automatically start running your script before doing anything else. No "
"files on the internal flash or attached SD card will be looked at before "
"running your code. That said, your script can still determine if an SD "
"card is attached or not and read/write files. So, if you still want to be"
" able to execute generic scripts from the flash and/or sd card you can do"
" so."
msgstr ""
"一旦您将这个新的固件映像烧录到您的 OpenMV Cam "
"中，它将自动在执行任何其他操作之前运行您的脚本。在运行您的代码之前，不会查看内部闪存或连接的 SD "
"卡上的任何文件。也就是说，您的脚本仍然可以确定是否连接了 SD 卡，并读取/写入文件。因此，如果您仍希望能够从闪存和/或 SD "
"卡执行通用脚本，您可以这样做。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:55
msgid ""
"Only the a frozn ``boot.py`` and ``main.py`` will override MicroPython's "
"default search paths. For any imported scripts/modules a matching "
"script/module will override any other scripts/modules frozen in the "
"firmware. This allows you to quickly test changes in scripts/modules "
"without having to deploy a new firmware. To disable this behavior clean "
"the ``sys`` module search path."
msgstr ""
"只有固化的 ``boot.py`` 和 ``main.py`` 会覆盖 MicroPython "
"的默认搜索路径。对于任何导入的脚本/模块，匹配的脚本/模块将覆盖固件中固化的任何其他脚本/模块。"
"这允许您快速测试脚本/模块的更改，而无需部署新固件。要禁用此行为，请清除 ``sys`` 模块的搜索路径。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:61
msgid "How to protect your code"
msgstr "如何保护您的代码"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/production.rst:63
msgid ""
"Once you freeze your scripts into the firmware your code can only be "
"extracted by tools that can dump your OpenMV Cam's program flash (or if "
"you code in a back door vulnerability). All modern MCUs feature ways for "
"developers to protect their application from being read using debugging "
"tools. Right now, OpenMV does not offer a generic way for you to do this."
" We leave this up to you. However, rest assured. If you really need to "
"prevent anyone from seeing your scripts it's absolutely possible."
msgstr ""
"一旦您将脚本固化到固件中，您的代码只能被能够转储您的 OpenMV Cam 的程序闪存的工具提取（或者如果你在代码中设置了后门漏洞）。所有现代 "
"MCU 都提供了开发人员可以使用调试工具保护其应用程序免受读取的方式。目前，OpenMV "
"尚未提供一种通用的方式让您执行此操作。我们将此留给您自己处理。但请放心，如果您真的需要阻止任何人查看您的脚本，这绝对是可能的。"

